		</p>
		<p>
		  I am a highly <span class="text-orange-500">curious</span> individual! Currently this curiosity has driven me to build my own Auto Differentiation Tensor Library in Rust called <a target="_blank" class="cactus-link inline-block" href="https://github.com/italoaa/Rusty-Flow">Rusty Flow</a> to learning GPU programming in CUDA <a target="_blank" class="cactus-link inline-block" href="https://github.com/italoaa/Mnist-from-scratch">Mnist from Scratch</a>. 
