		I constantly find new ways of challenging myself, growing my knowledge and nourishing personal spirit. This sometimes drives me crazy ... sometimes
		</p>
		<p>
			If you want to know what I am up to look at my <a
				aria-label="github"
				class="cactus-link inline-block"
